text: Jiří Fiřt (born 1 August 1972) is a Czech gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Czech Republic Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
